{"tid":2002214,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"永續黃色經濟：成為藍絲都難以抗拒的黃店","createTime":"2020-05-05T05:22:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T16:54:55.000Z","uid":48083,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b0e86b0b99d44297382e5b21f4dc6c754880f901","tid":2002214,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T05:22:57.000Z","msg":"戴穎姿<br />\n<br />\n自從 2019 年 6 月，黃藍之別演變成黑白良心的分野，幫襯藍店等同經濟上支持盲目撐警的族群。然後，我們吃力地發展出「黃色經濟圈」這個概念。<br />\n<br />\n請留意，要堅守這概念，是「吃力」的。<br />\n<br />\n不知道你們有沒有試過：某幾間藍店在被定義為藍色之前，其實你很愛亦很常光顧。最顯然而見的是餐廳，好食與不好食，很好食所以喜歡幫襯，就是這樣簡單。<br />\n<br />\n像我本人，對南記粉麵的春卷小窩米線有股狂熱，它甚至是我的 comfort food ；生活中遇上令人抓狂的時刻，立即就嘴饞，好想馬上來碗大辣米線。 <br />\n<br />\n後來南記爆出是撐警藍店，至今我都沒有再食南記。然而，這種拒絕光顧是非常刻意的，明明自己就心心念念、希望可以再食南記，但礙於立場，每一次經過南記都要努力克制自己，不好落入對家的美食圈套。<br />\n<br />\n值得思考的問題就來了：何以「黃色經濟圈」需要苦苦持守？<br />\n<br />\n有麝自然香，何須迎風立。一間店家，如果做得足夠好，不必宣傳、不必告急，自自然然就客似雲來。更甚是，客源也不一定局限於黃絲&mdash;&mdash;藍絲素來以沒骨氣沒原則見稱，店家的質素能達至連藍絲都禁不住要幫襯，本人愚見，方才是永續「黃色經濟圈」之道。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/personal/%E6%B0%B8%E7%BA%8C%E9%BB%83%E8%89%B2%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F-%E6%88%90%E7%82%BA%E8%97%8D%E7%B5%B2%E9%83%BD%E9%9B%A3%E4%BB%A5%E6%8A%97%E6%8B%92%E7%9A%84%E9%BB%83%E5%BA%97/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpersonal%2F%25E6%25B0%25B8%25E7%25BA%258C%25E9%25BB%2583%25E8%2589%25B2%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F-%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%2582%25BA%25E8%2597%258D%25E7%25B5%25B2%25E9%2583%25BD%25E9%259B%25A3%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E6%258A%2597%25E6%258B%2592%25E7%259A%2584%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%25BA%2597%2F&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktXGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=5948308b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpersonal%2F%25E6%25B0%25B8%25E7%25BA%258C%25E9%25BB%2583%25E8%2589%25B2%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F-%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%2582%25BA%25E8%2597%258D%25E7%25B5%25B2%25E9%2583%25BD%25E9%259B%25A3%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E6%258A%2597%25E6%258B%2592%25E7%259A%2584%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%25BA%2597%2F&h=9f487fbd\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/personal/%E6%B0%B8%E7%BA%8C%E9%BB%83%E8%89%B2%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F-%E6%88%90%E7%82%BA%E8%97%8D%E7%B5%B2%E9%83%BD%E9%9B%A3%E4%BB%A5%E6%8A%97%E6%8B%92%E7%9A%84%E9%BB%83%E5%BA%97/</a>"},{"pid":"002a8d113e218e7603e14f23cec5244361b5c3ff","tid":2002214,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T05:24:28.000Z","msg":"大部份藍絲本身就色盲唔會抵制"},{"pid":"d0ca4d7977277c9e6a6436e88ffb91ebe7e4608f","tid":2002214,"uid":240004,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T05:32:18.000Z","msg":"班藍絲有著數就狗衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n早排黃店搞醫護優惠 不知幾多藍絲仆去買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be749f654370affe29da43ac5fb31fe375cd0a73","tid":2002214,"uid":95138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T05:33:57.000Z","msg":"連登仔：叫藍絲鬥藍"},{"pid":"708379ea0019a39fc1d18a7d47dddbe9b5075380","tid":2002214,"uid":59973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T05:35:25.000Z","msg":"食店以外呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ab982f345bec4dcf060e731470c9eaca6eae52","tid":2002214,"uid":257516,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T05:40:27.000Z","msg":"事實係 難食黃店係辜負緊用心經營黃店嘅心血<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好心班兒登仔唔好盲撐難食黃店 做臭自己個朵"},{"pid":"99bcad340d25ac1c174ed87692ed37fb930fdbe4","tid":2002214,"uid":165336,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T05:43:27.000Z","msg":"有d暗黃店大把藍屍唔知照食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用和你et搵過一暗黃店語又捐錢又派水<br />\n上到去零文宣不過好食<br />\n果時非繁忙老細出黎問d野岩唔岩食<br />\n貼佢吹幾句我話上網搵黃店先知有間係度<br />\n佢即刻「薯～～～明架啦唔好係度講」<br />\n其實我地好需要呢種要刻意查先搵到既黃店黎吸納敵人資源"},{"pid":"bca88b34dad7e148e343a6ee2d83b63141d82bd2","tid":2002214,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T05:44:19.000Z","msg":"關於黃色經濟圈，我有d野想講：<br />\n<br />\n我想講翻其實黃色經濟圈最核心精神係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>紅死藍貧，紅死是為了打擊支共呢個恐怖份子籌集資金。藍唔洗死，但要慘比其他綠絲睇，就係為左&ldquo;統戰&rdquo;綠絲，壯大黃色經濟圈。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n所以大家幫襯黃店之外亦要記得先紅後藍：<br />\n<br />\n1.切斷中國國企在香港經營獲得外匯收入的機會，以加速支爆。<br />\n2.令藍絲企業經營困難，&ldquo;統戰&rdquo;綠絲企業<br />\n舉例，呢個原則點樣用：<br />\n基於先紅後藍原則，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">銀行方面一定係先中銀後匯豐</span></strong><br />\n根據先紅後藍原則，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">應該先Pacific(華潤)後Starbucks（美心）</span></strong><br />\n基於先紅後藍原則，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>&ldquo;幫襯&rdquo;紅店力度不應該比藍店細。尤其各種隱性紅店係支共既重要回血劍</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9d28397586c508e05add5ef2079735f7be338c65","tid":2002214,"uid":165336,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T05:45:27.000Z","msg":"更正：<br />\n有d暗黃店大把藍屍唔知照食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用和你eat搵過一暗黃店話佢又捐錢又派水<br />\n上到去零文宣不過好食<br />\n果時非繁忙老細出黎問d野岩唔岩食<br />\n同佢吹幾句我話上網搵黃店先知有間係度<br />\n佢即刻「薯～～～明架啦唔好係度講」<br />\n其實我地好需要呢種要刻意查先搵到既黃店黎吸納敵人資源"},{"pid":"32149d1d2ba27e1fb90170489acb11a9a36eff78","tid":2002214,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d28397586c508e05add5ef2079735f7be338c65","tid":2002214,"uid":165336,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T05:45:27.000Z","msg":"更正：<br />\n有d暗黃店大把藍屍唔知照食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用和你eat搵過一暗黃店話佢又捐錢又派水<br />\n上到去零文宣不過好食<br />\n果時非繁忙老細出黎問d野岩唔岩食<br />\n同佢吹幾句我話上網搵黃店先知有間係度<br />\n佢即刻「薯～～～明架啦唔好係度講」<br />\n其實我地好需要呢種要刻意查先搵到既黃店黎吸納敵人資源"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T05:48:38.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n好需要暗黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e3129f3bc6d8f72b9eda2e08867b188519a7acc","tid":2002214,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T14:35:41.000Z","msg":"藍屍唔會點理你顏色"},{"pid":"514965980ce7d70c1f2364f1d0ec36f5bc592435","tid":2002214,"uid":201732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T16:54:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}